content: I'm not sure about the specific region or state in India my parents are from, but I do know that they moved to the US when they were in their early twenties. I'm interested in learning more about the cultural practices and traditions that are common in India, such as festivals, food, and customs. I've grown up with some Indian traditions in my household, like celebrating Diwali and eating Indian food, but I want to learn more about the stories and history behind them.
